---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Terms of Service — Sarif Consulting"
  description="Terms of Service for Sarif Consulting — the governing terms for use of our website, engagements and consulting services. Portland, Oregon."
>
  <section class="policy-hero section" aria-label="Terms of Service header">
    <div class="container policy-hero-inner">
      <p class="section-label">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="section-header">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="policy-meta">Last updated: April 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="policy-body section cv-auto" data-cv-size="xl" aria-label="Terms of Service content">
    <div class="container policy-content page-reads-over-lobby">

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2 class="policy-heading">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>
          By accessing this website (<a href="https://sarifconsulting.ai" class="policy-link">sarifconsulting.ai</a>)
          or engaging the services of Sarif Consulting, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service.
          If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use this site or engage our services.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2 class="policy-heading">2. Services</h2>
        <p>
          Sarif Consulting provides AI-augmented consulting services including research and strategic
          analysis, web development, strategic materials production and content and communications.
          The specific scope, deliverables, timeline and compensation for each engagement are
          defined in a separate written agreement between Sarif Consulting and the client.
        </p>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to decline any engagement at our discretion and without obligation
          to provide a reason.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2 class="policy-heading">3. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          Unless otherwise specified in a written engagement agreement, all deliverables produced
          by Sarif Consulting for a client become the property of the client upon receipt of full
          payment. Sarif Consulting retains no license to use, reproduce, or reference client
          deliverables without explicit written authorization.
        </p>
        <p>
          All content on this website&mdash;including text, graphics, design elements and code&mdash;is
          the property of Sarif Consulting and may not be reproduced, distributed, or used without
          prior written permission.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2 class="policy-heading">4. Confidentiality</h2>
        <p>
          Sarif Consulting treats all client project details, communications and deliverables as
          strictly confidential. We do not disclose client work publicly without explicit written
          consent. Clients agree to treat any proprietary methodologies, processes, or non-public
          information shared by Sarif Consulting as confidential.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2 class="policy-heading">5. Payment Terms</h2>
        <p>
          Payment terms are defined in individual engagement agreements. Unless otherwise agreed
          in writing, invoices are due within fourteen (14) days of issuance. Sarif Consulting
          reserves the right to pause or discontinue work on an engagement in the event of
          non-payment.
        </p>
        <p>
          All fees are quoted in United States Dollars (USD) unless otherwise specified.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2 class="policy-heading">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          Sarif Consulting provides services and deliverables to the best of its ability and
          professional judgment. However, we do not warrant that any deliverable will achieve
          a specific business outcome, secure funding, win an election, or produce any particular
          result. Clients retain full responsibility for decisions made based on our work.
        </p>
        <p>
          To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, Sarif Consulting&rsquo;s total liability
          for any claim arising from or related to an engagement shall not exceed the total fees
          paid for that engagement.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2 class="policy-heading">7. Warranties and Representations</h2>
        <p>
          This website and its contents are provided &ldquo;as is&rdquo; without warranties of any kind,
          express or implied. Sarif Consulting does not warrant that the website will be uninterrupted,
          error-free, or free of harmful components.
        </p>
        <p>
          Sarif Consulting makes no representations regarding the accuracy, completeness, or
          timeliness of any third-party information referenced in deliverables. All research
          deliverables cite sources and are produced with rigorous verification, but clients are
          responsible for independently confirming any data before making consequential decisions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2 class="policy-heading">8. Use of AI Tools</h2>
        <p>
          Sarif Consulting employs AI meta-orchestration as a core component of its production
          methodology. Deliverables are produced under the judgment and editorial oversight of
          human architects and do not constitute outputs generated without human review. We are
          transparent about our methodology and will discuss the role of AI in any engagement
          upon request. Upon request, we will specify which components of a deliverable involved
          AI-assisted generation, to the extent practical for the engagement and subject to confidentiality
          obligations.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2 class="policy-heading">9. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>
          These Terms of Service are governed by the laws of the State of Oregon, United States,
          without regard to conflict of law principles. Any disputes arising from these terms or
          from an engagement with Sarif Consulting shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction
          of the courts of Multnomah County, Oregon.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2 class="policy-heading">10. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We may update these Terms of Service periodically. Updates will be reflected on this
          page with a revised date. Your continued use of this website or engagement of our
          services following any update constitutes acceptance of the revised terms.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section policy-contact">
        <h2 class="policy-heading">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about these Terms of Service may be directed to:<br />
          <a href="mailto:info@sarifconsulting.ai" class="policy-link">info@sarifconsulting.ai</a>
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .policy-hero {
    padding-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .policy-hero-inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .policy-meta {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    opacity: 0.6;
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  /* Body */
  .policy-body {
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .policy-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .policy-section {
    margin-bottom: 52px;
    padding-bottom: 52px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.06);
  }

  .policy-section:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .policy-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(0.8rem, 1.2vw, 1rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--cyan-bright);
    text-shadow: var(--cyan-glow-text);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .policy-content p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .policy-content p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .policy-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 16px 0 20px 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .policy-list li {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.75;
    padding-left: 20px;
    position: relative;
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .policy-list li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 10px;
    width: 6px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--cyan-core);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .policy-list li strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .policy-link {
    color: var(--cyan-core);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.4);
    transition: color 0.2s ease, text-decoration-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .policy-link:hover {
    color: var(--cyan-bright);
    text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.7);
  }

  .policy-link:focus {
    outline: none;
  }

  .policy-link:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--cyan-core);
    outline-offset: 3px;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .policy-contact {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
    padding: 40px;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .policy-link {
      transition: none;
    }
  }
</style>
